<figureCitation box="[588,735,1020,1046]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="4.[161,198,1315,1337]" captionTargetBox="[177,1039,169,1272]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[167,1072,138,1305]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Fig. 4. — Bambara spp. Bambara fragilis sp. n., A, habitus; Ba, Bb, spermathecae. Bambara lyrae sp. n., C, habitus; D, spermatheca.?Bambara problematica Darby, E, spermatheca.?Bambara subjoannis Darby, F, spermatheca. Bambara magnifica Darby, G, spermatheca. Bambara gabela Darby, H, spermatheca. Bambara frosti (Dybas), I, spermatheca." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3653792" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3653792/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="244">Figs 4C, 4D</figureCitation>
